<div class="legacy-para">MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; I don't know if they just heard what I said, but I hope it was received well.</div>
<div class="legacy-para">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Okay.&nbsp; Second, the budget bills are going to be rolled out this week, as well.&nbsp; And I</div>
<div class="legacy-para">wonder if now you can talk about how appropriate you feel it would be to do a national</div>
<div class="legacy-para">health plan with reconciliation language so that it couldn't filibustered.</div>
<div class="legacy-para">MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; Well, look, I think the debate on reconciliation is months and months and months</div>
<div class="legacy-para">ahead of itself.&nbsp; I think if anybody is concerned about how this is going to be resolved,</div>
