<div class="legacy-para">notion that people in this town ought to be able to work together to find solutions to some</div>
<div class="legacy-para">of our biggest problems.</div>
<div class="legacy-para">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; But on that, what some Republicans -- Judd Gregg, for instance -- are saying that if</div>
