<div class="legacy-para">fail to get some bipartisan deal, then always fall back and --</div>
<div class="legacy-para">MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; Let me -- two points on that.&nbsp; One is, I think that gives, again, short shrift</div>
<div class="legacy-para">to the notion that people should have good ideas about a problem we've talked about for</div>
<div class="legacy-para">several decades; there isn't a lack of good ideas out there.&nbsp; And the second thing I might</div>
