<div class="legacy-para">certain level or percentage of spending relating to their GDP, as was mentioned -- as the</div>
<div class="legacy-para">IMF suggested.&nbsp; But I believe that what was agreed on at that meeting was to continue to</div>
<div class="legacy-para">monitor what might be needed to stimulate economies in order to address the downturn in</div>
<div class="legacy-para">production that each economy will see as part of a global recession.</div>
