<div class="legacy-para">Sorry, go ahead.</div>
<div class="legacy-para">Q&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; What's the President hoping to communicate tomorrow night with the press conference?</div>
<div class="legacy-para">MR. GIBBS:&nbsp; Well, I think as he's done over the past -- certainly the better part of the</div>
